features: SUITABLE LUGGAGE: Suitable for 18-32 inch luggage. The 10-piece storage bag can basically hold the items which a person's needed for 7-10 day trip. Can be used with the usual 26-32 inch Luggage.

MATERIAL: Made of high-quality thicker polyester fabric (the new 290T double-sided twill fabric). Mesh top panel for easy identification of contents and well separate different clothes as you like. Light weight, washable. Durable& soft, easy to fold up, extremely portable, high performance for Waterproof and tear resistant.

SET INCLUDES: Luggage organizer set includes 3 Packing Cubes ( Large:10-12 shirts, Medium:7-9 Shirts, Small: 4-6 shirts)+1 Underwear Bag+1 Shoes Bag+2 Drawstring Bag+1 Cosmetic Bag+1 Toiletry Bag+1 Flat Bag. Easily pack all your luggage in your suitcases, carry-on bags, drawers and backpacks, ideal for travel, family vacations, business trips, outdoor camping and daily storage.

10 DIFFERENT SIZE BAG: 3 Mesh Packing Cube: (L: 15.8"x12.2"x4.3", M: 12.2"x11"x4.3", S: 12.2"x7.9"x4.3"); 1 Underwear Bag: (11" x 7.9" x 4.3"); 1 Shoes Bag:(13.8" x 10.6"); 2 Drawstring Bag: (M:13.8" x 10.6", S:10.2"x 6.7"); 1 Cosmetic Bag: (10.2"x5.9"x3.5"); 1 Toiletry Bag: (9.4"x7.8"x3.1"); 1 Flat Bag: (10.2" x 5.9"). They are manually sewn, there sizes will be some Error, the Error we control in the ± 0.8(in).

GREAT WAY TO KEEP ORGANIZED: Your 10 piece set fits like a glove most airline carry-on suitcases, tote, weekender, backpacks and duffel bags. Great way to keep organized for Family breaks, business travel, backpacking, camping, hiking, rv, cruise holidays & saddlebags.
body.description: Best Choose:* Sort And Find Your Things In A Flash!* Save Your Clothes From Stains, wrinkles and damages!* Pack More In Less Space!* Unpack Your Things In A Breeze!* Check-Out Has Never Been Easier!* Pack your luggage quickly, easily and securely with the Travel Organizers!* Provide different sizes of products by yourself!* Light travel is a pleasure, travel bags make you more convenient on the way!Packing List:1. Large Cubes: suitable for 2 winter clothes or 3-4 sets spring and autumn clothes.2. Medium Cubes: suitable for 6-8 spring and autumn clothes or 2-3 bath towels, 4-5 towels.3. Small Cubes: suitable for 4-5 small clothes or other small travel items.4.Underwear Bag: suitable for 4-5 bras and close fitting clothes.5. Medium Drawstring Bag: suitable for bath towel or towel or other foldable items.6. Small Drawstring Bag: suitable for socks and other small items.7. Flat Pocket: suitable for mobile phones, power packs, data cables, certificates, bills and other important items.8. Shoe Bag: suitable for storing all kinds of shoes below 42 yards, such as slippers, sports shoes, casual shoes, flat shoes, etc.9. Mesh Cosmetic Bag: suitable for toiletries and skin care products10. Hanging Hook Toiletries Bag: toiletries and cosmetics required for daily travel and business travel can be handled in one package.Washing: wash at water temperature below+30 °, do not soak, gently machine wash, hand wash, hang to dry, do not dehydrate.Note:1.
